full_summary:
### Environmental Chambers Tender Announcement

**Reference Number:** CB-4460-25119599

**Amendment Number:** 6

**Solicitation Number:** W6399-23-LM88/A

The Government of Canada has issued a Request for Proposal (RFP) to solicit bids for the procurement of two (2) environmental chambers, with options for an additional three (3). This acquisition aims to provide laboratory environmental conditioning equipment that meets the requirements of the Department of National Defence.

**Key Tender Information:**

* **Tender Closing Date:** 2023-06-02T14:00:00
* **Expected Contract Start Date:** 2023-07-03
* **Expected Contract End Date:** 2026-07-03
* **Regions of Opportunity:** Canada
* **Regions of Delivery:** Canada

**commercial and Trade Agreements:**
This tender is open to contractors who are compliant with the following trade agreements:
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* North American Free Trade Agreement (NAFTA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement

**improvement and Notice Requirements:**
Bidders are responsible for ensuring they have made themselves aware of all relevant amendments to the tender. Tender notice documents are available online. Suppliers interested in participating in this procurement should register in the Buy and Sell Supplier section of the Canadabuys website. For any questions or clarifications on this tender, please contact the contracting entity representative indicated below.

**procurement Point of Contact:**
Phone: (613) 998-4714
Email: [Donna.Lowes@forces.gc.ca](mailto:Donna.Lowes@forces.gc.ca)
Release Date: 2023-03-28
Location: Ottawa, Ontario
### Document Attachments
A variety of related documents including the tender description document is available on the Canadabuys website.
